org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.things

Class VeluxProductReference

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openhab.binding.velux.internal.things.VeluxProductReference

  • @NonNullByDefault
public class VeluxProductReference
extends java.lang.Object
    Velux product characteristics: Product Reference.

    Combined set of information which describes a current state of a single Velux product.

    Methods in handle this type of information:
    • getProductName() to retrieve the name representing this actuator/product.
    • getProductType() to retrieve the type of the product.
    • toString() to retrieve a human-readable description of the product state.
    Author:
    Guenther Schreiner - initial contribution.
